##A2n insider interview | Dan Qing: The Faint Voice of Reason & Communication in the volunteer team

Micro Signal Anti

Features A2n, Anti-2019-ncov. A group of folk volunteers whose main work is to popularize science and dispel rumors.

On January 20,2020, the epidemic in Wuhan quickly escalated. Groups and groups of young people act spontaneously, online or offline for the fight against the epidemic to contribute their own strength. Anti-2019-ncov (A2n Epidemic Situation Volunteer Group) is one of them.
A2N has opened up a group, Materials Group, Translation Group, popular science and other 11 groups. So far, many volunteers from all over the country have joined A2n. Although the Sparrow is small, complete, in order to let the A2n in this era of low-light stay a little longer, A2N depth project group for everyone to bring A2n internal interview series.

This week's interviewees:
Translation group-in-depth content group-coordination Group-danqing

On January 20,2020, the epidemic in Wuhan quickly escalated. Groups and groups of young people act spontaneously, online or offline for the fight against the epidemic to contribute their own strength. Anti-2019-ncov (A2n Epidemic Situation Volunteer Group) is one of them.

A2N has opened up a group, Materials Group, Translation Group, popular science and other 11 groups. So far, many volunteers from all over the country have joined A2n. Although the Sparrow is small, complete, in order to let the A2n in this era of low-light stay a little longer, A2N depth project group for everyone to bring A2n internal interview series.

This week's interviewees:

Translation group-in-depth content group-coordination Group-danqing

A2N.
Dan Qing, who works on the A2N translation team

A2N.

Dan Qing, who works on the A2N translation team

For Danqing, the story of joining A2n and taking on the job was less dramatic. As the epidemic quietly escalated and quickly heated up in the sphere of public opinion, Danqing, like many young people, was worried about what was happening in Wuhan, and he was looking for an opportunity to do something about it. Just at this time, Danqing just joined the formation of the "A2N-3 groups of volunteers. ". His first impression of A2n is just a lot of people, some chaotic work, everyone in the group talking about the situation, the direction of work is not clear.

Chinese Odyssey 2002 by ECHO

Many have retreated, feeling he can not Carry so many strangers, and wondering what to do, while he observes patiently where the nascent group needs him. Soon after, A2n set up a translation team to translate practical information in foreign languages and release it to the public, and he immediately applied to join, taking his first step in A2n's work. He used his experience to position himself as a proofreader and publishing operator. It was late January, a time of rising social panic, when most people were home for the holidays, and many students with different professional backgrounds were involved in their work, eventually forming a large team in the translation team. After returning to work and school recently, there are still many volunteers active.
Translating is not easy, especially when the translation team is faced with articles from natural science journals such as nature and the Lancet, in which even students with relevant academic backgrounds are baffled by the various technical terms, each paper is translated from the beginning to the proofreader, and the team members discuss and refine their choice of words in the group. At the beginning, most of the output of the translation group is medical literature, reading threshold is so high that the volume of reading transmission is relatively low, to a certain extent, affected the enthusiasm of the group members. Since then, the translation team has added translations of articles on Social Science Research and analysis related to the epidemic, which has rekindled readers'interest and stimulated the team to work more efficiently. Danqing found that, after changing the theme, each translation material sent to the group is usually translated and proofread within a few minutes of the initiative claimed, almost no need to mobilize to achieve seamless workflow links.

We are glad that the high quality content of the translation team did not drown in the flood of information during the epidemic, but stood out from the rest of the world. Recently, A2n translated popular science information of the micro blog has exceeded 2000 followers, douban number has also been close to 2000, reflecting the reader's recognition of the content.

When it comes to the greatest significance of translation information, Dan Qing mentioned an interesting description: listening to both sides of the Ming Dynasty. In Modern Society, he argues, people are faced with seemingly diverse information in all directions, but are not good at identifying complementary or contradictory information to form their own judgments. In the end heard a lot of truth, but still can not say their own ideas, let alone carry out the corresponding action. The translation team's job is to bring these "stones from other mountains" into the public space, to help netizens to hear some voices from different channels, but at the same time with a professional voice, thus helping people to look at the problem rationally and objectively.

On the other hand, Danqing is well aware that the number of readers the team can reach is not even the tip of the iceberg for Chinese netizens, and the improvement of judgment requires individuals to master multi-dimensional skills and experience. The highly specialized and professional background of Modern Society often causes adults to stick to one part of their job, and over time pass the judgment and responsibility to technical experts. When technologists are unable to intervene quickly and directly because of resource constraints and problems, such self-isolation can lead to panic and loss of control. Non-medical Translation Group partners try to challenge the Unfamiliar Medical Literature, it is just a way out of their own professional limitations. Of course, articles must be reviewed by volunteers with a medical background before they are published. The humanities graduate himself has read several medical articles in Nature and is trying to learn and understand them, and is beginning to be able to extract key information from the literature.

The rapid development of society requires people not only to master more and more fine professional knowledge, but also to be familiar with multi-domain knowledge and have the ability to absorb new information quickly, this is inconsistent with the idea of requiring everyone to "specialize" . We still need to have a profound discussion about this concept of learning. However, consistency does not affect the work of the translation team, because one more person can "listen to both sides" , then even the darkest corner can not obscure the light of rational thinking.

A2N.
The communication secrets of Danqing

The communication secrets of Danqing

Of course, as a temporary group of online volunteers, staff fitting and docking is always the most difficult issue. The translation team faced similar travails in its early years. By the end of January, though, the team had finished translating a number of articles, but some workflow issues were still pending in the operational phase. If the normal frequency of release, then a lot of information will be too long to lose time, and affect the team members continue to work enthusiasm. To this end, Danqing and another person in charge of more than 2 hours of consultations, the establishment of a new workflow, immediately release the backlog of information and resume work progress. He reflected that the two men should have agreed on this earlier if they wanted to avoid it. But because communication is so important, it is well worth the time it took to communicate and adjust the demands as a corrective measure.

This is a picture taken by Dan Qing. He named it "everything has a soul, heaven and man are one" 

Dan Qing not only in the translation group to assume the role of communication and coordination, in the A2n large team, he has also been playing a tandem role for the partners. A2N recently opened a group-style operation of the depth of the project team, many departments will be absorbed into a group of thematic activities. This plan dilutes the manpower of some departments, and increases the workload for many volunteers, and reconstructs the partial workflow. To this end, as the head of the in-depth Project Team, Danqing spent a lot of time communicating with department heads and volunteers, explaining to them the significance of developing in-depth content, and consulting the composition of the staff.

For a volunteer team like A2n, he takes on one of the most difficult but essential tasks of all: leading to a shared vision. The members of the temporary team come from all over the world, everyone has his own opinion, and are not willing to be forced to work in volunteer activities.

It's not easy to come up with a blueprint, but it's even more time-consuming to clarify ideas with people of different identities. During the initial phase of the project, Danqing spent a lot of time coordinating communication almost every day and gradually accepted the value of deep projects that promote thinking and produce personal reflection. He is working on a deep project to get his A2n pals to dig into the details of life in the epidemic, such as the situation of foreigners who stayed in China during the disaster. The content is relevant to life, the cost to members to access the relevant content is not high, but also play a volunteer group from all corners of the country advantage. This weak bond, like Lu Xun's light, wavers in the dark but never annihilates, illuminating each other.

What is more, from the initial concept submitted by the sponsor, to identify the theme and material, to build the participation model, every step will be in-depth participation and consultation project model. For example, in the discussion on "the trolley problem and the human disaster —— The film "The flu" , Danqing and the initiator set a clear discussion topic and theme a week in advance, that is to contact the film during the epidemic prevention measures and human issues to reflect and summarize. Moreover, they anticipated the social and negative consequences of early reflection on the epidemic, thus setting the topic of online conversation more precisely. These preliminary matting and the full discussion, all guarantees the netizen when participates in the film conversation to be able smoothly to melt into the topic and expresses the opinion.

It is because of this consideration that the current in depth content has been well advanced, and I believe that in the future they can provide a number of unique and meaningful perspectives for epidemic reflection. Danqing also noted that the workshops, photo exhibitions, and in depth tweets that are involved in his current projects are experienced in his daily work, so he is very clear about what each project is ultimately intended to deliver, each communication progress can also be targeted to guide the initiator, and not to advance too fast or slip up.

A2N.
"You can be light, too. "

"You can be light, too. "

At the end of the conversation, when I asked Danqing why he had worked so hard on the project, he just smiled and said, "I just felt that some of the work in the team wasn't being done, so I naturally took the lead. "

I asked him again: "Do you sometimes feel particularly powerless to reflect so much on the epidemic and read so much about it every day? "

"No, as pessimistic as I am about the impact of the epidemic, I am never powerless. If we feel powerless, we simply don't know what to do because we've read too few books or have too little information. I believe that everyone can find opportunities to contribute and make a difference through learning and participation. So I feel energetic every day,"he said naturally and firmly.

I thought back to his words after the interview, untimely recalling the Classic Line from the Ultraman Tiga Finale: "You can be light, too. "
